results.name: Regular triangle where T(n,k) is the number of non-isomorphic connected multiset partitions of weight n with multiset density -1 <= k <= n-2.
comment: The multiset density of a multiset partition is the sum of the numbers of distinct vertices in each part minus the number of parts minus the number of vertices.
xref: First column is A321229. Row sums are A007718.
results.author: _Gus Wiseman_, Nov 01 2018
